  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nStar Atlas : Never Alone – A year’s worth of promises\nPockThePirate posted a video about the Never Alone campaign.\nStar Atlas : Updates and Upcoming Releases – Ship Destruction Atlas Star 18\nPockThePirate posted a video with some Star Atlas updates.\nMetaverse Nomads #95 Star Atlas w/ Krigs and Signal\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nSTAR ATLAS #181 DEVELOPER UPDATE #18\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video with Star Atlas updates.\nBeginner Overview of Play.StarAtlas.com\nGladiator posted a video overview of the Star Atlas website.\nStar Atlas Flight Trainer Race! 4k\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video of the Star Atlas flight trainer.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #80\nAephia published their latest Star Atlas newsletter.\n50 SHIP GIVEAWAY!!! Star Atlas\nGladiator posted a video of a Star Atlas ship giveaway.",
